  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you reach 7th level, your body begins to adapt to toxins and venoms, ignoring their corrupting effects. You gain advantage on saving throws you make to avoid or end the poisoned condition on yourself. You also have resistance to poison damage.</p><p>Additionally, you can trigger a burst of adrenaline that lets you temporarily resist the negative effects of a mutagen. As a bonus action, you can ignore the negative side effect of one mutagen affecting you for 1 minute. Once you do so, you cannot do so again until you finish a long rest, unless you take necrotic damage equal to one roll of your hemocraft die. This damage cannot be reduced in any way.</p>",
